# Contacts Module — FROZEN

**Frozen:** 2026-06-23 (develop branch)

The Contacts module (Suppliers + Customers) is approved for freeze. Do not modify Contacts-related code without explicit user approval.

## Scope

### Supplier
- CRUD, status (active/inactive), soft delete, restore
- Required bank accounts (at least one non-empty row)
- Profile photo, card front/back document uploads with storage cleanup
- Mobile registry and `SUP-` code sequencing
- Compact single-row list toolbar (search, inline filters, More Filters dropdown, Add on right)

### Customer
- CRUD, soft delete, restore
- Optional bank accounts
- Profile photo document upload with storage cleanup
- Mobile registry and `CUS-` code sequencing
- Same list toolbar UX pattern as Supplier

### Shared
- Mobile uniqueness per `contactable_type` (same mobile allowed on 1 supplier + 1 customer)
- Role-based permissions via `users.role` (`super_admin` | `staff`)
- `ContactMobileNumber` morph registry

## Permissions

| Action | Staff | Super Admin |
|--------|-------|-------------|
| View / Create / Edit | Yes | Yes |
| Delete / Restore | No | Yes |
| Supplier inactive | No | Yes |

## Operational queries for future modules

```php
Supplier::operational()->orderBy('business_name');
Customer::query()->orderBy('customer_name'); // excludes soft-deleted by default
```

## Out of scope (deferred)

- Full Roles & Permissions module
- Ledger account auto-link on create
- Product Catalog (next module)

## Supersedes

Replaces the earlier Supplier-only freeze rule. Both modules ship together.
